ApplicationContext context = new AnnotationConfigApplicationContext(CollegeAppConfig.class);

In this case we are specify only one class 'CollegeAppConfig.class' then
container load only "CollegeAppConfig.class" class annotation class.

that why @ComponentScan comes into picture

when IOC container found @ComponentScan then it will load then classes
which we specify in the @ComponentScan and specified class should annotated
with @Component annotation.